data.description: Wow! Be the proud owner of this turnkey 2-story home featuring mature trees, a 2-car garage, RV gate, & a delightful front porch! elegant interior includes neutral paint, tile flooring & soft carpet, chic light fixtures, plantation shutters, & a well-sized living & dining room. Continue onto the family room equipped w/a media niche & Arcadia doors to the patio. The gorgeous kitchen offers recessed lighting, built-in appliances, granite counters, a pantry, wood cabinetry w/crown moulding, & an island w/a breakfast bar. Upstairs, the sizable loft w/shelves & built-in desk is ideal for a study area. Owner's suite boasts plush carpet, vaulted ceilings, a pristine ensuite w/dual sinks, & a walk-in closet. The large backyard, w/ its covered patio & fragrant citrus trees, is the perfect place for spending quality time w/ friends and loved ones! Truly a must-see!
